title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight/map feature, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export should proceed successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight/map feature.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception that is thrown.
